sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Tenant User
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant BG as BackgroundTask
    participant DK as Docker

    U->>API: POST /api/v1/tasks/execute
    API->>DB: create task + task_runs(PENDING)
    API-->>U: task_id + status=PENDING
    API->>BG: enqueue task execution
    BG->>DB: task RUNNING
    loop per instance
        BG->>DB: check instance status
        alt instance RUNNING
            BG->>DK: docker exec script
            BG->>DB: task_run SUCCESS/FAILED + stdout/stderr
        else STOPPED/invalid
            BG->>DB: task_run FAILED (Instance is not RUNNING)
        end
    end
    BG->>DB: aggregate task status (SUCCESS/FAILED/PARTIAL_SUCCESS)

